## LCA & Circularity Analysis

### Business Problem

Organizations face increasing pressure to reduce product-level environmental impacts, improve resource efficiency, and strengthen sustainability performance across manufacturing and supply-chain systems. However, many lack analytical tools for evaluating lifecycle emissions, material tradeoffs, and circularity opportunities.

### Solution

Developed lifecycle assessment (LCA) and circularity analytics workflows to evaluate product carbon footprints, material scenarios, emissions hotspots, and sustainability tradeoffs across manufacturing and resource systems.

### Tools

openLCA | Python | Excel | LCA Modeling | Sustainability Analytics

### Strategic Insights

* Identified lifecycle emissions hotspots across material and production stages
* Evaluated lower-carbon and resource-efficient material alternatives
* Improved visibility into circularity and sustainability performance opportunities

